title: I Knew You Were Trouble (Taylor’s Version)
description:
Taylor ignored the red flags and went head first and fearless into this troubled relationship. Who is the inspiration behind this song? And what connections can be made to other songs? Plus, more merch store ideas, the podcast names that didn’t make the cut…. And why didn’t we get this specific version? Ana, Lacey, Amy and Nick break it all down!
